{"tid":2209681,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"用光時頭像遭停課 擬海外升學  香島手足「學校冇得限制思想」","createTime":"2020-09-19T19:16:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T08:33:57.000Z","uid":240362,"like":454,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"e5d1045e1d5fa66d33be433336bc08890feb8d89","tid":2209681,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T19:16:10.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】香島中學中四生Gary（化名）因為在網上課堂頭像使用「光時」口號相片，遭校方勒令停課一周及建議考慮轉校。他近日透露，家人已為他申請休學，現積極考慮到海外繼續學業。Gary接受本報訪問時說，他在內地長大、中一才來港，但過去一年的經歷令他視香港為家，志願更由警察改為記者。<br />\n<br />\n遭校方勒令停學後，Gary至今心情仍未平復，但沒為當日的行為感後悔，「你（學校）覺得我用icon（頭像）顛覆國家，但我覺得只係張平凡新聞照片」。他預料重回香島「機會不大」，因家人已為他申請休學，並建議他轉校或到海外升學，學校亦已經停用其所有網上學習賬戶。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200920/TBOJOHWMPVBC3E6UXP36IVS2FI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200920%2FTBOJOHWMPVBC3E6UXP36IVS2FI%2F&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxE38q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=ffaa5165\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200920%2FTBOJOHWMPVBC3E6UXP36IVS2FI%2F&h=3432a5b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200920/TBOJOHWMPVBC3E6UXP36IVS2FI/</a>"},{"pid":"c8fb131cc440426cb366392a4dfe7193b1485b8a","tid":2209681,"uid":21545,"like":208,"dislike":2,"score":206,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T19:21:40.000Z","msg":"你都係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a52c23c9ac39a11e0e1a4d2f2bb9bb1e6322a77","tid":2209681,"uid":74442,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T19:22:08.000Z","msg":"有志氣"},{"pid":"547ab2fd0e8ffd9f0ccc390c0e53cb6b5a601121","tid":2209681,"uid":209773,"like":91,"dislike":0,"score":91,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T19:22:11.000Z","msg":"垃圾學校"},{"pid":"958cc8d822c2e4335