0f57307d57f7","tid":2209681,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T00:03:50.000Z","msg":"垃圾學校唔讀也罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支持手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過出國讀書咪好金<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8f8e10af0b6e2c1fd69adaf259f96ad7b3c573c","tid":2209681,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1127bf08195b133d31bd335148b6b7d2b50cdcd8","tid":2209681,"uid":293097,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T21:43:19.000Z","msg":"香島回歸前已經係紅底<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下年中一就唔好入去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香島中學是由參加抗日戰爭後撤港的知識份子甘偉光、楊夷、朱治平、吳炳昌、潘比薇、方紹謙、黃建峰私人出資於1946年在九龍窩打老道創立，<span class=\"red\">聘請中國共產黨黨員知識份子盧動為第一任校長</span>。手書體校名「香島中學」系初年兼任客座教員之中國著名學者郭沫若所提寫。翌年於運動場道另租新址作為中學部，原址留作小學部。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T00:35:25.000Z","msg":"d支那狗既名永遠都咁7<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6984d152c718ce10bdf384c6a073402824c5168d","tid":2209681,"uid":306689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e5d1045e1d5fa66d33be433336bc08890feb8d89","tid":2209681,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T19:16:10.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】香島中學中四生Gary（化名）因為在網上課堂頭像使用「光時」口號相片，遭校方勒令停課一周及建議考慮轉校。他近日透露，家人已為他申請休學，現積極考慮到海外繼續學業。Gary接受本報訪問時說，他在內地長大、中一才來港，但過去一年的經歷令他視香港為家，志願更由警察改為記者。<br />\n<br />\n遭校方勒令停學後，Gary至今心情仍未平復，但沒為當日的行為感後悔，「你（學校）覺得我用icon（頭像）顛覆國家，但我覺得只係張平凡新聞照片」。他預料重回香島「機會不大」，因家人已為他申請休學，並建議他轉校或到海外升學，學校亦已經停用其所有網上學習賬戶。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200920/TBOJOHWMPVBC3E6UXP36IVS2FI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200920%2FTBOJOHWMPVBC3E6UXP36IVS2FI%2F&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxE38q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=ffaa5165\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200920%2FTBOJOHWMPVBC3E6UXP36IVS2FI%2F&h=3432a5b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200920/TBOJOHWMPVBC3E6UXP36IVS2FI/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T00:39:09.000Z","msg":"大家要記住唔係香港出世一樣可以係有共同價值觀手足，所以不要以貌取人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e44efd0b2c0bf4f1fc13fa99e6c71b1c8d4da964","tid":2209681,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T00:41:08.000Z","msg":"吃子文化的教畜"},{"pid":"87975c85dec338915997bb3828fbd41abd8f2eb3","tid":2209681,"uid":306689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34fd6d7c477b6217f8dbdbc66e5592cff10fa03f","tid":2209681,"uid":24345,"like":61,"dislike":0,"score":61,"quote":{"pid":"8b2e4937823d8177ecba8f52bb1ce42e6831b02b","tid":2209681,"uid":361247,"like":3,"dislike":30,"score":-27,"quote":{"pid":"5b9b088ac488eb7afa2c1750fd46e0f2072ec520","tid":2209681,"uid":312744,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T20:28:12.000Z","msg":"中一才來港<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T20:53:46.000Z","msg":"原來又係支那新移民但黃既"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T21:20:31.000Z","msg":"根本最藍嗰忽肯定係土生土長香港人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T00:42:37.000Z","msg":"班人唯利是圖有奶便是娘，根本無顏色丶無道德底線只有錢同權力慾。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae0a52437126e4dde1d28ae27f4bdefbab14b59","tid":2209681,"uid":229880,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T00:48:08.000Z","msg":"有共同價值觀嘅就係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc2e4a68f678d9a808309a692055f7911f7a3392","tid":2209681,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T00:54:32.000Z","msg":"遭校方勒令停課一周及建議考慮轉校<br />\n間學校有咩資格"},{"pid":"6f276ded711769b4a97b16a1d9d7ac99c79d8113","tid":2209681,"uid":195877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d8